text: Enterprise Rancheria is the landbase for the Estom Yumeka Maidu Tribe, located in Butte County, near Oroville, California. The nearest outside communities are Berry Creek and Forbestown. As of the 2010 Census the population was 1. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Maidu Category:Geography of Butte County, California Category:Federally recognized tribes in the United States
